commit.message: chore(makefile) Print full diff when testing.

test(python) Explicitely test base & native.

This patch removes the `try`/`except` block, so that we see when there
is an issue with the native implementation. It is then possible to
test the base and native algorithms explicitely.

feat(python) Avoid Wasm function lookups in native.

By writing `fn = instance.exports.fn`, we can use `fn` without any
lookup in the Wasm exported functions list.
fix(python) Fix missing `os` import in native implementation.
